snowcovered lines british rail said it had only two snowplow 
locomotives for 10000 miles of track it was considered a waste of 
money to buy more when the country did not have heavy snow every 
winter the staterun network said 
six people were expected to appear before magistrates monday in 
coventry england where looters stole jewelry clothes and stereos 
while police car patrols were halted by snow later officers were 
sent out on foot 
