asked his old foreman and coworkers to be my support 
i am going to return here often and i am going to do 
everything for you he told workers i know where i have this 
white shirt from and i know that my overalls here were the same as 
yours sometimes even dirtier 
walesa carried every province according to unofficial results 
tyminski did best in rural areas where farmers are discontented 
with economic reforms that nolonger guarantee a minimum price for 
