discounted to 1500 but most remain in the 25003000 range 
in the united states they cost less than 500 
a 14inch color monitor for a home computer made in brazil and 
thus for sale legally costs 2800 the us price is 650 
brazils topoftheline laser printer costs 20000 a us 
model with the same features sells for 3500 
