henry v cbsfox home video vhsbeta 9298 rated pg 
 
when an example of artistic excellence reaches the screen it is 
a time for celebration so break out the cristal kenneth branaghs 
henry v has reached the home video market 
a spare wellcrafted interpretation of the play by william 
shakespeare branaghs movie focuses on the complex young king 
rather than the pagentry and expansiveness of the conflict between 
french and english 
