back of the seat watching two lawyers debate a minor point in a 
preliminary hearing 
people know charlestons most famous resident is down at the 
courthouse today even in west virginias biggest city population 
63000 word spreads fast 
but they leave him alone aside from the judge the defendant 
two court officers and the lawyers hes studying the actors got 
the room to himself 
no fans demanding his attention no producers demanding his 
time no costars demanding he watch them strut their stuff and 
except briefly no reporters demanding details of his life 
and thats why nolte who works on the fringe of hollywoods 
imageobsessed film industry and skirts the edge of stardom finds 
himself more at home in the hills of west virginia than in los 
angeles or new york 
this whole business concept of stardom its a thing i find 
very entrapping very limiting and not worth a damn he said i 
really dont function at all in my thinking on that level 
nolte was busy filming cape fear martin scorseses remake 
of the 1962 gregory peckrobert mitchum film in which an exconvict 
blames a lawyer for his sentence and threatens the lawyers wife 
nolte plays the lawyer who defends and betrays robert de niro 
he researched much of the role in his adopted hometown spending 
several days haunting the kanawha county courthouse and jail to 
observe lawyers and judges at work 
i want to see the demeanor of a lawyer i want to see how he 
