94 moves to another state based on 1988 census figures 
researchers say that translates to 275000 to 400000 moves a year 
golant sees the primary impacts on housing because the migrants 
need new places to live and on recreation and leisure 
everything from golfing to vacations because they have the 
free time the money and generally good health 
